                            <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.3">
                                                             
                                <locus from="76r"/>
                                <title type="complete" ref="LIT2711Mark"/>
                                <textLang mainLang="gez"/> 
                                
                                <explicit type="subscriptio" xml:lang="gez">
                           <locus target="#121v"/>ተጽሕፈ፡ በዛመነ፡ ማቴዎስ፡ ወንጌላዊ፡ እንዘ፡ 
                                    <date>ዓመት፡ ምሕረት፡ ፸፻ወ፩ ፻፶ወ፯ዓመት፡</date> እምፍጥረት፡ ዓለም። እምአመ፡ ነግሠ፡ መፍቀሬ፡ እግዚአበሔር፡ ን ፧ ሥ ፧፡
                                    ..... ፡<date> ፴ወ፱ዓመት</date> ፤ ወአጽሐፈ፡ በብዙኅ፡ ፃማ፡ ሶበ፡ አስትናስኦ፡ ፍቅር፡ መ ንፈሳዊ፡ ወሥዕልሂ፡ ዘዓረቢ፡ ገብረ፡ መ ፧ ገለ፡ ግዕዝ።</explicit>
                                <note>The year 7157 of the subscription corresponds with AD 1664/1665, but the 34th year of the reign 
                                    of <persName ref="PRS4015Fasilada">Fāsiladas</persName> (whose name has been erased) was AD 1667. The MS seems therefore to have been written in 1667/1668.</note>
                                
                            </msItem>
                            
